---
import '/src/styles/global.css'
import { ClientRouter, fade } from 'astro:transitions';
import '@fontsource/mulish'
---

<html lang="pt-br">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Juan | Portfolio</title>
		<ClientRouter/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<nav class="navegacao">
				<ul class="menu">
					<li>
						<a transition:animate={fade({ duration: '0.1s' })} transition:name="projetos" class="menu-link" href="/projetos">Projetos</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a transition:animate={fade({ duration: '0.1s' })} transition:name="blog" class="menu-link" href="/blog">Blog</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a transition:animate={fade({ duration: '0.1s' })} class="menu-link" href="/contato" transition:name="contato">
							Contato
						</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</nav>
		</header>
		<main>
			<div class="conteudo">
				<div class="nome">Juan &lt;coder&gt;</div>
				<div class="texto-principal">
					<div class="efeito-linha"></div>
					<p>Sou desenvolvedor full-stack, <br> que escreve c√≥digos elegantes, limpos e eficientes.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<footer></footer>
	</body>	
</html>

<script>
	document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
		document.body.classList.remove('linha-animada');
		void document.body.offsetWidth;
		document.body.classList.add('linha-animada');
	});
</script>

<style>
	* {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

	html {
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		background-color: #17181C;
		color: white;
	}

	.navegacao {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 15px;
		z-index: 100;
		height: 90px;
	}

	.menu {
		font-family: "Mulish";
		display: flex;
		gap: 80px;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 500;
		padding: 15px;
	}

	.menu-link {
		position: relative;
		padding: 0.5rem;
	}

	.menu-link::after {
		content: '';
		height: 2px;
		position: absolute;
		width: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d31ff7, rgba(186, 82, 255, 0.533));
		transition: width 0.5s ease;
	}

	.menu-link:hover::after {
		width: 100%;
	}

	.conteudo {
		font-family: "Mulish";
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		height: 100vh;
	}

	.efeito-linha {
		height: 0px;
		width: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d31ff7, rgba(186, 82, 255, 0.533));
		transition: height 0.7s ease-in-out;
	}

	.nome {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.texto-principal {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 20px;
	}

	body.linha-animada .efeito-linha {
		height: 50px;
	}

</style>

